Investment Banking & Capital Markets





 
								 
									
								
									Print
								
							
						 





   Leadership in investment banking  





You expect your investment bank to understand your company and industry inside and out. With Wells Fargo Securities, you get that – and much more.  We take the time to listen and learn about your business — growth opportunities, challenges, and operations. We combine this informed perspective with our product knowledge and market expertise to work with you and your team on a vision for your business, and we have the capital strength to help support your goals.



		   Industry Expertise



		   Products and Services



		   Recent Transactions



		   Market Leadership




As your trusted advisor in investment banking, we provide strategic and capital markets expertise, advice, and execution for public finance, real estate, and the following industries:

 Consumer & retail  Our consumer and retail team provides industry knowledge and expertise to advice companies across the following industry sectors:  Consumer and retail Energy and power Financial institutions Gaming Healthcare Industrials Media and education Technology Telecommunications and infrastructure      Energy & power  Our energy and power team provides industry knowledge and expertise to advice companies across the following industry sectors:  Upstream Midstream Service & supply Major integrated power Downstream Merchant power Renewables Propane Liquid natural gas Electric & gas distributor Integrated electric utility      Financial institutions  Our financial institutions team provides industry knowledge and expertise to advice companies across the following industry sectors:  Asset management Depositories & banks Insurance Specialty finance Exchanges & market structure     Financial sponsors  The financial sponsors group provides corporate and investment banking services to the private equity industry. We collaborate with our industry and product specialists to provide advice and execution for their portfolio companies, from acquisition ideas and financing to eventual monetization through an initial public offering or sale.    Gaming  Our gaming team provides industry knowledge and expertise to advise companies across the following industry sectors:  Land-based hotels/casinos Riverboat casinos Native American casinos Gaming equipment manufacturers      Healthcare  Our healthcare team provides industry knowledge and expertise to advise companies across the following industry sectors:  Biopharmaceuticals Medical products Healthcare services  Alternate site/outsourcing Facilities Drug stores Information technology Real estate investment trusts (REIT) Long-term care Managed care Pharmaceutical outsourcing/distribution Physician practice management       Industrials  Our industrials team provides industry knowledge and expertise to advise companies across the following industry sectors:  Building products & homebuilding Forest products & packaging Chemicals Metals & mining Capital goods Diversified services Defense, aerospace & technology services Transportation & logistics      Media & education  Our media and education team provides industry knowledge and expertise to advise companies across the following industry sectors:  Traditional media Diversified media, entertainment & leisure Education  Tech-enabled services Software & technology Publishing & content Corporate training/lifelong learning       Technology  Our technology team provides industry knowledge and expertise to advise companies across the following industry sectors:  Business & transaction services  Financial technology Business & information services   Systems Internet & digital media Software Semiconductors Clean technology     Telecommunications & infrastructure  Our telecommunications and infrastructure team provides industry knowledge and expertise to advise companies across the following industry sectors:  Cable Data center/hosting & tower infrastructure Wireline/wireless    


Our product specialists work closely with our industry bankers to deliver expert advisory services. We also provide comprehensive origination and underwriting across the equity and debt capital markets.

 Advisory services Our advisory services include:  Mergers & acquisitions Quantitative corporate finance Financial restructurings Strategic alternative assessments Private placements Ratings advisory Defense advisory Fairness opinions Liability management    Equity capital markets Our capabilities in the equity capital markets include:  Primary and secondary common stock offerings Initial public offerings At-the-market offerings Convertible securities Market risk management     Debt capital markets Our capabilities in the debt capital markets include:  High grade offerings Leveraged finance offerings Preferred stock offerings Syndicated loans Asset-backed finance and securitization Market risk management   


     



Wells Fargo Securities ranks in the top 10 in all capital markets sectors and has been ranked #3 in total number of U.S. investment banking transactions for each of the past seven years.1
Some additional examples of our leadership in the credit markets include: 

#1 in high grade trading2
#1 lead arranger of asset-based loans1
