Securities & Markets





 
								 
									
								
									Print
								
							
						 





   Insights and resources to help you navigate the global marketplace  





We provide institutional clients, alternative asset managers, and large corporations with a comprehensive approach to the sales, trading, structuring, and execution of a wide variety of financial market products, including bonds, equities, market-linked products, clearing services, and risk management. 

Equities and Investment Solutions
Make more informed investment decisions with access to corporate-client management teams, customized investments, and trade execution strategies.

Equities and Investment Solutions 


Fixed Income Sales & Trading
Choose the fixed income products and services that are right for your portfolio, including corporate debt, market-linked investments, municipal products, money-market securities, and U.S. government securities.

Fixed Income Sales & Trading 


Foreign Exchange Services
As one of North America’s leading foreign exchange services providers, Wells Fargo has a variety of foreign currency services and solutions for corporate customers.
Foreign Exchange Services



Institutional Investor Services
Delivering coordinated services to help alternative asset managers and other institutional investors execute their investment strategies, mitigate their risk, and grow their assets.

Institutional Investor Services 


Market Risk Management
Protect your business by managing exposure to changes in interest rate, foreign currency, commodities, equities, and credit markets.

Market Risk Management 


WATS® Electronic Trading Services
Execute multi-asset class electronic trading strategies through a variety of venues with our complete suite of e-trading services.

WATS® Electronic Trading Services 




 Wells Fargo Securities is the trade name for the capital markets and investment banking services of Wells Fargo & Company and its subsidiaries, including but not limited to Wells Fargo Securities, LLC, a member of NYSE, FINRA, NFA, and SIPC, Wells Fargo Prime Services, LLC, a member of FINRA, NFA and SIPC, and Wells Fargo Bank, N.A. Wells Fargo Securities, LLC and Wells Fargo Prime Services, LLC are distinct entities from affiliated banks and thrifts.   Investment and Insurance Products:  Are Not insured by the FDIC or any other federal government agency Are Not deposits of or guaranteed by a Bank May Lose Value  




